* Estimate NEER daily
* Compute deviation vs midband
* Long SGD when near lower bound, short SGD when at upper band

### 7.2 **Global Electronics Cycle Positioning**

* Long SGD when semi upcycle starts
* Short SGD when global IT demand collapses

